WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.000
الحمد بالله رب العالمين

00:00:04.000 --> 00:00:07.000
الرحمن الرحيم

00:00:07.000 --> 00:00:10.000
مالك يوم الدين

00:00:10.000 --> 00:00:14.000
إياك نعبد وإياك نستعيم

00:00:14.000 --> 00:00:17.000
اهدن الصراة المستقيم

00:00:17.000 --> 00:00:21.000
صراة الذين أنعنت عليهم

00:00:21.000 --> 00:00:24.000
غير المغضوب عليهم

00:00:24.000 --> 00:00:35.260
السلام عليكم ورحمة الله وبركاته

00:00:35.260 --> 00:00:37.260
بسم الله الرحمن الرحيم

00:00:37.260 --> 00:00:38.260
الحمد لله رب العالمين

00:00:38.260 --> 00:00:40.260
وبه نستعين ونصلي ونسلم

00:00:40.260 --> 00:00:42.260
على أفضل الخلق أجمعين

00:00:42.260 --> 00:00:45.260
نبينا محمد وعلى آله وصحبه واتابعين

00:00:45.260 --> 00:00:49.260
ومن تبعهم بإحسان إلى يوم الدين وبعد

00:00:49.260 --> 00:00:51.260
All praises due to Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala

00:00:51.260 --> 00:00:53.260
blessings and salutations upon

00:00:53.260 --> 00:00:55.260
محمد صلى الله عليه وسلم

00:00:55.260 --> 00:00:57.260
may Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala bless him

00:00:57.260 --> 00:00:59.260
and his entire household

00:00:59.260 --> 00:01:00.260
all his companions

00:01:00.260 --> 00:01:02.260
may Allah bless them and bless every single one of us

00:01:02.260 --> 00:01:04.260
and grant us goodness

00:01:04.260 --> 00:01:06.260
beloved brothers and sisters in Islam

00:01:06.260 --> 00:01:10.260
yesterday we were making mention of the story

00:01:10.260 --> 00:01:12.260
where there was an accusation

00:01:12.260 --> 00:01:14.260
leveled against the most pure of women

00:01:14.260 --> 00:01:16.260
Aisha radiallahu anha

00:01:16.260 --> 00:01:19.260
and just to recap as to exactly what had happened

00:01:19.260 --> 00:01:23.260
as they were returning from the battle of Banu al-Mustaliq

00:01:23.260 --> 00:01:27.180
the prophet salallahu alaihi wasallam

00:01:27.180 --> 00:01:29.180
decided to instruct the army to leave

00:01:29.180 --> 00:01:31.180
and Aisha radiallahu anha

00:01:31.180 --> 00:01:35.180
was looking for a bracelet of hers or a necklace

00:01:35.180 --> 00:01:37.180
and at that time

00:01:37.180 --> 00:01:39.180
they used to have a haudaj

00:01:39.180 --> 00:01:41.180
in the Arabic language the haudaj is

00:01:41.180 --> 00:01:43.180
the cover at the top of the animal

00:01:43.180 --> 00:01:45.180
or at the top of the camel

00:01:45.180 --> 00:01:47.180
where the women folk used to sit

00:01:47.180 --> 00:01:50.180
as the camel used to move

00:01:50.180 --> 00:01:52.180
it used to protect them from the sun

00:01:52.180 --> 00:01:55.180
as well as act as privacy for them

00:01:55.180 --> 00:01:58.180
and when they stopped at a specific place

00:01:58.180 --> 00:02:01.180
the camel would be made to sit down

00:02:01.180 --> 00:02:04.180
the men would lift up the entire haudaj

00:02:04.180 --> 00:02:05.180
and put it to the side

00:02:05.180 --> 00:02:08.180
which would make it look like a little tent

00:02:08.180 --> 00:02:10.180
and thereafter they would go away

00:02:10.180 --> 00:02:12.180
and the women would then either come out

00:02:12.180 --> 00:02:14.180
or remain in there and so on

00:02:14.180 --> 00:02:16.180
be protected from the sun and what have you

00:02:16.180 --> 00:02:18.180
so Aisha radiallahu anha says

00:02:18.180 --> 00:02:20.180
as they had put it down

00:02:20.180 --> 00:02:23.180
and I was doing some of my things

00:02:23.180 --> 00:02:24.180
whatever I had to do

00:02:24.180 --> 00:02:26.180
I realized that I was missing a necklace

00:02:26.180 --> 00:02:28.180
and I went hunting for it

00:02:28.180 --> 00:02:29.180
looking for it around

00:02:29.180 --> 00:02:31.180
and the prophet salallahu alaihi wasallam

00:02:31.180 --> 00:02:33.180
instructed the army to leave

00:02:33.180 --> 00:02:35.180
they lifted up this haudaj

00:02:35.180 --> 00:02:38.180
thinking that Aisha radiallahu anha was inside

00:02:38.180 --> 00:02:39.180
they placed it on the camel

00:02:39.180 --> 00:02:40.180
and they progressed

00:02:40.180 --> 00:02:42.180
and she says when I got back

00:02:42.180 --> 00:02:44.180
to the place where they were

00:02:44.180 --> 00:02:45.180
I noticed there was no one

00:02:45.180 --> 00:02:46.180
everyone had gone

00:02:46.180 --> 00:02:48.180
and I told myself that perhaps

00:02:48.180 --> 00:02:50.180
they will notice my absence

00:02:50.180 --> 00:02:51.180
and they will return

00:02:51.180 --> 00:02:54.180
but sadly they did not return

00:02:54.180 --> 00:02:55.180
the army continued

00:02:55.180 --> 00:02:58.180
and this was after the battle of Banu al-Mustalik

00:02:58.180 --> 00:02:59.180
after some time

00:02:59.180 --> 00:03:01.180
one of the sahaba radiallahu anhum

00:03:01.180 --> 00:03:02.180
was passing from the path

00:03:02.180 --> 00:03:04.180
and Aisha radiallahu anha says

00:03:04.180 --> 00:03:05.180
I was dressed in black

00:03:05.180 --> 00:03:06.180
I was quite tired

00:03:06.180 --> 00:03:09.180
I was sitting down on the floor

00:03:09.180 --> 00:03:11.180
meaning on the desert sand

00:03:11.180 --> 00:03:14.180
and I had fallen off to sleep

00:03:14.180 --> 00:03:17.180
and I got up by someone saying

00:03:17.180 --> 00:03:19.180
inna lillahi wa inna ilayhi raji'oon

00:03:19.180 --> 00:03:22.180
as I looked it was Safwan ibn al-Mu'attal

00:03:22.180 --> 00:03:23.180
radiallahu anhu

00:03:23.180 --> 00:03:24.180
he did not utter one word

00:03:24.180 --> 00:03:26.180
he had understood already

00:03:26.180 --> 00:03:29.180
that this is umul mu'mineen

00:03:29.180 --> 00:03:31.180
Aisha radiallahu anha

00:03:31.180 --> 00:03:33.180
and she has been left behind

00:03:33.180 --> 00:03:36.180
by the entire caravan as they left

00:03:36.180 --> 00:03:40.180
so he allowed his camel to be seated

00:03:40.180 --> 00:03:42.180
and he got her onto it

00:03:42.180 --> 00:03:43.180
and he took her all the way

00:03:43.180 --> 00:03:44.180
to al-Madeen al-Munawwara

00:03:44.180 --> 00:03:45.180
as they arrived

00:03:45.180 --> 00:03:47.180
Abdullah ibn Ubayy ibn Salul

00:03:47.180 --> 00:03:49.180
who was the head of the hypocrites

00:03:49.180 --> 00:03:52.180
who had during the battle of Banu al-Mustalik

00:03:52.180 --> 00:03:56.180
made mention of something very strange

00:03:56.180 --> 00:03:57.180
he said

00:03:57.180 --> 00:04:00.180
la irraja'na ila al-Madeenati

00:04:00.180 --> 00:04:04.180
layukhrijanna al-a'zoo minhal athal

00:04:04.180 --> 00:04:06.180
when we get to Madina Munawwara

00:04:06.180 --> 00:04:09.180
the superior will kick out the inferior

00:04:09.180 --> 00:04:11.180
meaning we are going to fix Muhammad

00:04:11.180 --> 00:04:14.180
a'udhu billah sallallahu alayhi wa sallam

00:04:14.180 --> 00:04:17.180
and we will see how we will remove him out

00:04:17.180 --> 00:04:18.180
and we made mention yesterday

00:04:18.180 --> 00:04:20.180
of Usaid ibn Hudayr

00:04:20.180 --> 00:04:21.180
and the other companions who said

00:04:21.180 --> 00:04:23.180
oh messenger sallallahu alayhi wa sallam

00:04:23.180 --> 00:04:26.180
you are the superior and he is the inferior

00:04:26.180 --> 00:04:29.180
so this man had had a plan in his head

00:04:29.180 --> 00:04:30.180
whatever the plan was

00:04:30.180 --> 00:04:35.180
this gave him reason to make something else up as well

00:04:35.180 --> 00:04:38.180
and so when he saw Aisha radiallahu anha

00:04:38.180 --> 00:04:40.180
enter Madina Munawwara

00:04:40.180 --> 00:04:41.180
with Safwan ibn al-Mu'attal

00:04:41.180 --> 00:04:44.180
he immediately started spreading a rumor

00:04:44.180 --> 00:04:46.180
that these two have committed the sin

00:04:46.180 --> 00:04:49.180
may Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala protect us all

00:04:49.180 --> 00:04:50.180
may He grant us goodness

00:04:50.180 --> 00:04:52.180
may He protect us in our offspring

00:04:52.180 --> 00:04:55.180
and may He really protect our tongues as well

00:04:55.180 --> 00:04:57.180
so this rumor began

00:04:57.180 --> 00:05:00.180
and Aisha radiallahu anha did not know about it at all

00:05:00.180 --> 00:05:01.180
she didn't even hear

00:05:01.180 --> 00:05:02.180
she went home

00:05:02.180 --> 00:05:05.180
and it continued in the sense that

00:05:05.180 --> 00:05:07.180
outside the house people started talking

00:05:07.180 --> 00:05:10.180
and the people were divided into three categories

00:05:10.180 --> 00:05:11.180
three major categories

00:05:11.180 --> 00:05:14.180
one of them those who invented the lie

00:05:14.180 --> 00:05:17.180
the head was Abdullah ibn Ubay ibn Salun

00:05:17.180 --> 00:05:18.180
they created it

00:05:18.180 --> 00:05:19.180
they knew it was just a rumor

00:05:19.180 --> 00:05:22.180
which they had started with evil intent

00:05:22.180 --> 00:05:23.180
the second group

00:05:23.180 --> 00:05:24.180
the second group

00:05:24.180 --> 00:05:27.180
those like Abu Ayub al-Ansari radiallahu anhu

00:05:27.180 --> 00:05:29.180
he told his wife Ummu Ayub

00:05:29.180 --> 00:05:31.180
he says oh Ummu Ayub

00:05:31.180 --> 00:05:33.180
could you ever do something like that

00:05:33.180 --> 00:05:34.180
she said never

00:05:34.180 --> 00:05:35.180
well if you cannot

00:05:35.180 --> 00:05:37.180
Aisha is cleaner than you

00:05:37.180 --> 00:05:38.180
Allahu Akbar

00:05:38.180 --> 00:05:39.180
so it's definitely a lie

00:05:39.180 --> 00:05:41.180
and we are clean

00:05:41.180 --> 00:05:43.180
we would believe she is even cleaner than us

00:05:43.180 --> 00:05:45.180
so they immediately threw out the statement

00:05:45.180 --> 00:05:47.180
and they refused to utter it

00:05:47.180 --> 00:05:48.180
and they said

00:05:48.180 --> 00:05:50.180
we believe that if we are pure

00:05:50.180 --> 00:05:52.180
she is even purer

00:05:52.180 --> 00:05:54.180
radiallahu anhu jami'an

00:05:54.180 --> 00:05:56.180
that was one category of people

00:05:56.180 --> 00:05:58.180
the other category of people were those

00:05:58.180 --> 00:06:00.180
who had spread the lie

00:06:00.180 --> 00:06:01.180
they did not create it

00:06:01.180 --> 00:06:02.180
but they spread it

00:06:02.180 --> 00:06:03.180
they spoke about it

00:06:03.180 --> 00:06:05.180
did you hear the latest gossip and so on

00:06:05.180 --> 00:06:09.180
now this is typical in our scenario nowadays

00:06:09.180 --> 00:06:10.180
what happens to us

00:06:10.180 --> 00:06:13.180
we find for some reason

00:06:13.180 --> 00:06:16.180
we find sweetness in words and in statements

00:06:16.180 --> 00:06:19.180
where rumor is being spread about others

00:06:19.180 --> 00:06:21.180
may Allah safeguard us

00:06:21.180 --> 00:06:24.180
so this is why we have a lesson to learn from this

00:06:24.180 --> 00:06:27.180
and inshallah we will get to it in a few moments

00:06:27.180 --> 00:06:29.180
so the Prophet sallallahu alaihi wasallam

00:06:29.180 --> 00:06:30.180
heard about it

00:06:30.180 --> 00:06:31.180
and he was very upset

00:06:31.180 --> 00:06:34.180
he went into Aisha radiallahu anhu's room

00:06:34.180 --> 00:06:35.180
several times

00:06:35.180 --> 00:06:37.180
and he would just ask her

00:06:37.180 --> 00:06:38.180
kayfateekum

00:06:38.180 --> 00:06:39.180
which means

00:06:39.180 --> 00:06:41.180
how is that one

00:06:41.180 --> 00:06:42.180
he is talking to her

00:06:42.180 --> 00:06:43.180
instead of saying how are you

00:06:43.180 --> 00:06:44.180
he is saying how is that one

00:06:44.180 --> 00:06:46.180
referring to her in absence

00:06:46.180 --> 00:06:48.180
showing a distance between him and her

00:06:48.180 --> 00:06:50.180
how is that one

00:06:50.180 --> 00:06:51.180
imagine you talking to your wife

00:06:51.180 --> 00:06:53.180
and you saying how is that one

00:06:53.180 --> 00:06:54.180
how are you

00:06:54.180 --> 00:06:55.180
Allahu Akbar

00:06:55.180 --> 00:06:56.180
so this was him

00:06:56.180 --> 00:06:57.180
he was upset

00:06:57.180 --> 00:06:58.180
but this is how he showed it

00:06:58.180 --> 00:07:00.180
sallallahu alaihi wasallam

00:07:00.180 --> 00:07:01.180
and at the same time

00:07:01.180 --> 00:07:03.180
he knew that it could either be a lie

00:07:03.180 --> 00:07:05.180
or it could be true

00:07:05.180 --> 00:07:07.180
although he knew within his heart

00:07:07.180 --> 00:07:08.180
that this is a lie

00:07:08.180 --> 00:07:10.180
but for him to come out and say

00:07:10.180 --> 00:07:11.180
this is a lie

00:07:11.180 --> 00:07:12.180
people would think

00:07:12.180 --> 00:07:13.180
you are defending your wife

00:07:13.180 --> 00:07:14.180
may Allah protect us

00:07:14.180 --> 00:07:16.180
so he had to wait for revelation

00:07:16.180 --> 00:07:19.180
for it to come with clarification

00:07:19.180 --> 00:07:21.180
to clear the name of Ummul Mu'mineen

00:07:21.180 --> 00:07:22.180
Aisha radiallahu anha

00:07:22.180 --> 00:07:24.180
but revelation did not come

00:07:24.180 --> 00:07:25.180
do you know why

00:07:25.180 --> 00:07:27.180
one of the reasons was

00:07:27.180 --> 00:07:29.180
that Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala

00:07:29.180 --> 00:07:32.180
kept this whole incident as a test

00:07:32.180 --> 00:07:35.180
in order to test everyone

00:07:35.180 --> 00:07:37.180
and in order for it to be a lesson for us

00:07:37.180 --> 00:07:39.180
who came later on

00:07:39.180 --> 00:07:40.180
generations down the line

00:07:40.180 --> 00:07:43.180
may Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala grant us a lesson

00:07:43.180 --> 00:07:45.180
so she was very very

00:07:45.180 --> 00:07:46.180
innocent of it

00:07:46.180 --> 00:07:47.180
she didn't even know

00:07:47.180 --> 00:07:48.180
why is the messenger

00:07:48.180 --> 00:07:49.180
salallahu alayhi wa sallam

00:07:49.180 --> 00:07:51.180
being so distant

00:07:51.180 --> 00:07:53.180
until one day she went out

00:07:53.180 --> 00:07:54.180
with one of her relatives

00:07:54.180 --> 00:07:56.180
known as Ummu Misthah

00:07:56.180 --> 00:07:59.180
the mother of Misthah ibn Athatha

00:07:59.180 --> 00:08:00.180
and when she went out

00:08:00.180 --> 00:08:02.180
this woman tells her

00:08:02.180 --> 00:08:04.180
ta'isa Misthah

00:08:04.180 --> 00:08:06.180
Misthah has definitely lost

00:08:06.180 --> 00:08:08.180
you know destruction upon Misthah

00:08:08.180 --> 00:08:10.180
so Aisha radiallahu anha

00:08:10.180 --> 00:08:11.180
looks at her and says

00:08:11.180 --> 00:08:13.180
how can you say that about someone

00:08:13.180 --> 00:08:15.180
who took part in the battle of Badr

00:08:15.180 --> 00:08:16.180
Misthah ibn Athatha

00:08:16.180 --> 00:08:18.180
Misthah ibn Athatha radiallahu anha

00:08:18.180 --> 00:08:20.180
he was a poor man

00:08:20.180 --> 00:08:23.180
who was related to Abu Bakr al-Siddiq radiallahu anha

00:08:23.180 --> 00:08:26.180
and Aisha was the daughter of Abu Bakr al-Siddiq radiallahu anha

00:08:26.180 --> 00:08:29.180
and Abu Bakr used to spend money on him

00:08:29.180 --> 00:08:31.180
and Abu Bakr al-Siddiq radiallahu anha

00:08:31.180 --> 00:08:33.180
who used to give him charities and look after him

00:08:33.180 --> 00:08:35.180
so Aisha is saying

00:08:35.180 --> 00:08:36.180
oh Ummu Misthah

00:08:36.180 --> 00:08:38.180
how can you say this about your own son

00:08:38.180 --> 00:08:41.180
when he has taken part in the battle of Badr

00:08:41.180 --> 00:08:44.180
and we made mention of the rank of the people

00:08:44.180 --> 00:08:46.180
who took part in the battle of Badr

00:08:46.180 --> 00:08:50.180
may Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala grant us also a rank

00:08:50.180 --> 00:08:52.180
through his mercy

00:08:52.180 --> 00:08:54.180
so she said didn't you hear

00:08:54.180 --> 00:08:56.180
what he is saying

00:08:56.180 --> 00:08:58.180
now Misthah was not from amongst those

00:08:58.180 --> 00:09:00.180
who invented the lie

00:09:00.180 --> 00:09:03.180
but he was one of those who was active in spreading it

00:09:03.180 --> 00:09:04.180
did you hear what happened

00:09:04.180 --> 00:09:05.180
and then he would tell someone

00:09:05.180 --> 00:09:06.180
did you hear what happened

00:09:06.180 --> 00:09:07.180
and then tell someone

00:09:07.180 --> 00:09:08.180
did you hear what happened

00:09:08.180 --> 00:09:09.180
and then tell someone

00:09:09.180 --> 00:09:13.180
so now when his mother told Aisha radiallahu anha

00:09:13.180 --> 00:09:14.180
she was shocked

00:09:14.180 --> 00:09:16.180
she went back home in tears

00:09:16.180 --> 00:09:18.180
the Prophet salallahu alaihi wasallam walked in

00:09:18.180 --> 00:09:19.180
same question

00:09:19.180 --> 00:09:20.180
kaifatikum

00:09:20.180 --> 00:09:22.180
how is that one

00:09:22.180 --> 00:09:23.180
she says oh messenger

00:09:23.180 --> 00:09:24.180
salallahu alaihi wasallam

00:09:24.180 --> 00:09:27.180
do you permit me to go to my parents home

00:09:27.180 --> 00:09:29.180
look at this word

00:09:29.180 --> 00:09:31.180
do you allow me to go home

00:09:31.180 --> 00:09:33.180
now she's understood what's happening

00:09:33.180 --> 00:09:36.180
do you allow me to go and see my mother and father

00:09:36.180 --> 00:09:38.180
so the Prophet salallahu alaihi wasallam permitted her to go

00:09:38.180 --> 00:09:41.180
she went in order to find out what to be done

00:09:41.180 --> 00:09:42.180
oh my mother

00:09:42.180 --> 00:09:43.180
have you heard what people are saying

00:09:43.180 --> 00:09:44.180
she said

00:09:44.180 --> 00:09:46.180
ummu ruman radiallahu anha

00:09:46.180 --> 00:09:48.180
the mother of Aisha radiallahu anha

00:09:48.180 --> 00:09:50.180
do you know

00:09:50.180 --> 00:09:53.180
when the Prophet salallahu alaihi wasallam later on

00:09:53.180 --> 00:09:55.180
spoke about ummu ruman

00:09:55.180 --> 00:09:56.180
the mother of Aisha

00:09:56.180 --> 00:09:59.180
he said whoever wants to see a hur from jannah

00:09:59.180 --> 00:10:01.180
look at ummu ruman

00:10:01.180 --> 00:10:02.180
subhanallah

00:10:02.180 --> 00:10:05.180
this was the mother of Aisha radiallahu anha

00:10:05.180 --> 00:10:07.180
so she speaks to her daughter

00:10:07.180 --> 00:10:09.180
saying oh my daughter

00:10:09.180 --> 00:10:11.180
don't worry don't get too

00:10:11.180 --> 00:10:13.180
overexcited about this rumour here

00:10:13.180 --> 00:10:14.180
meaning don't overreact

00:10:14.180 --> 00:10:15.180
leave it

00:10:15.180 --> 00:10:16.180
sometimes what happens

00:10:16.180 --> 00:10:18.180
someone who is good looking like you

00:10:18.180 --> 00:10:20.180
quite young like you

00:10:20.180 --> 00:10:21.180
subhanallah

00:10:21.180 --> 00:10:23.180
you may have people who spread things and so on

00:10:23.180 --> 00:10:26.180
don't read too deep into it ya Aisha

00:10:26.180 --> 00:10:28.180
so the mother is giving advice

00:10:28.180 --> 00:10:29.180
to her daughter

00:10:29.180 --> 00:10:31.180
subhanallah

00:10:31.180 --> 00:10:33.180
and Aisha radiallahu anha says no

00:10:33.180 --> 00:10:34.180
it's very difficult for me

00:10:34.180 --> 00:10:36.180
because here there is rumour spread

00:10:36.180 --> 00:10:38.180
the messenger salallahu alaihi wasallam is not speaking to me

00:10:38.180 --> 00:10:41.180
and Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala has not sent revelation

00:10:41.180 --> 00:10:43.180
and I am completely innocent

00:10:43.180 --> 00:10:45.180
the mother did not doubt the innocence of her daughter

00:10:45.180 --> 00:10:47.180
subhanallah

00:10:47.180 --> 00:10:50.180
and the father abu bakar as-siddiq radiallahu anhu

00:10:50.180 --> 00:10:51.180
what should he say

00:10:51.180 --> 00:10:54.180
he is a friend of rasoolullah salallahu alaihi wasallam

00:10:54.180 --> 00:10:56.180
as well as

00:10:56.180 --> 00:10:58.180
a father-in-law at the same time

00:10:58.180 --> 00:11:01.180
and he is a person who is a follower at the same time

00:11:01.180 --> 00:11:03.180
what should he say

00:11:03.180 --> 00:11:05.180
Allah and his messenger know best

00:11:05.180 --> 00:11:07.180
so this caused a lot of discomfort

00:11:07.180 --> 00:11:09.180
until the prophet salallahu alaihi wasallam

00:11:09.180 --> 00:11:11.180
many days later

00:11:11.180 --> 00:11:13.180
after continuing in this manner with Aisha radiallahu anha

00:11:13.180 --> 00:11:15.180
crying, rumours spreading

00:11:15.180 --> 00:11:18.180
people falling into several categories

00:11:18.180 --> 00:11:19.180
and so on

00:11:19.180 --> 00:11:21.180
and Aisha radiallahu anha

00:11:21.180 --> 00:11:23.180
says I couldn't even sleep properly

00:11:23.180 --> 00:11:25.180
and I couldn't even eat

00:11:25.180 --> 00:11:26.180
and I couldn't

00:11:26.180 --> 00:11:28.180
I really didn't even understand

00:11:28.180 --> 00:11:30.180
what was happening due to lots of crying

00:11:30.180 --> 00:11:31.180
and so on

00:11:31.180 --> 00:11:33.180
but all I knew is Allah would clear my name

00:11:33.180 --> 00:11:35.180
Allah would send revelation

00:11:35.180 --> 00:11:37.180
I was innocent, completely innocent

00:11:37.180 --> 00:11:38.180
so now

00:11:38.180 --> 00:11:40.180
the prophet salallahu alaihi wasallam decided

00:11:40.180 --> 00:11:42.180
to ask some of his companions

00:11:42.180 --> 00:11:45.180
because revelation did not come for more than a month

00:11:45.180 --> 00:11:47.180
so he calls Ali ibn Abi Talib

00:11:47.180 --> 00:11:50.180
and Usama ibn Zaid radiallahu anhum

00:11:50.180 --> 00:11:52.180
he says oh Ali, what do you think

00:11:52.180 --> 00:11:54.180
oh Usama, what do you think

00:11:54.180 --> 00:11:56.180
Usama ibn Zaid radiallahu anhu

00:11:56.180 --> 00:11:57.180
he says

00:11:57.180 --> 00:11:59.180
this is a fabrication

00:11:59.180 --> 00:12:00.180
that's what he says

00:12:00.180 --> 00:12:01.180
he says

00:12:01.180 --> 00:12:03.180
Aisha radiallahu anha

00:12:04.180 --> 00:12:06.180
she is clean, she is pure

00:12:06.180 --> 00:12:08.180
this is all the mischief of hypocrites

00:12:08.180 --> 00:12:09.180
and so on

00:12:09.180 --> 00:12:10.180
and Ali radiallahu anhu

00:12:10.180 --> 00:12:11.180
he says look

00:12:11.180 --> 00:12:13.180
she is a young lady

00:12:13.180 --> 00:12:15.180
there are many other women besides her

00:12:15.180 --> 00:12:16.180
why don't you ask

00:12:16.180 --> 00:12:18.180
the servant Barirah

00:12:18.180 --> 00:12:20.180
and see what she says

00:12:20.180 --> 00:12:22.180
so the prophet salallahu alaihi wasallam asks

00:12:22.180 --> 00:12:23.180
Barirah

00:12:23.180 --> 00:12:26.180
Barirah was the servant of Aisha radiallahu anha

00:12:26.180 --> 00:12:27.180
oh Barirah

00:12:27.180 --> 00:12:28.180
what do you think of this

00:12:28.180 --> 00:12:31.180
Barirah says wallahi it is false

00:12:31.180 --> 00:12:34.180
she is one of the most chaste women

00:12:34.180 --> 00:12:35.180
that you could have

00:12:35.180 --> 00:12:37.180
very clean, very pure

00:12:37.180 --> 00:12:40.180
and she went on praising her in her own words

00:12:40.180 --> 00:12:42.180
and Rasulullah salallahu alaihi wasallam then got up

00:12:42.180 --> 00:12:43.180
he was upset

00:12:43.180 --> 00:12:45.180
he went out where the Ansar were

00:12:45.180 --> 00:12:46.180
and he says

00:12:51.180 --> 00:12:53.180
who is going to excuse me

00:12:53.180 --> 00:12:55.180
who is going to excuse me

00:12:55.180 --> 00:12:57.180
regarding a person

00:12:57.180 --> 00:12:59.180
whose harm has now reached

00:12:59.180 --> 00:13:01.180
the innermost part of my own home

00:13:01.180 --> 00:13:03.180
which means Abdullah ibn Ubayy ibn Salul

00:13:03.180 --> 00:13:06.180
which means who can retaliate

00:13:06.180 --> 00:13:07.180
or who would excuse me

00:13:07.180 --> 00:13:09.180
if I were to retaliate

00:13:09.180 --> 00:13:11.180
Sa'd ibn Mu'adh radiallahu anhu gets up

00:13:11.180 --> 00:13:12.180
and says oh messenger

00:13:12.180 --> 00:13:13.180
who is he

00:13:13.180 --> 00:13:15.180
if he is from my clan

00:13:15.180 --> 00:13:16.180
I will execute him

00:13:16.180 --> 00:13:18.180
and if he is from the other clan

00:13:18.180 --> 00:13:19.180
you tell us what to do

00:13:19.180 --> 00:13:20.180
we will do it

00:13:20.180 --> 00:13:23.180
so immediately Sa'd ibn Ubada

00:13:23.180 --> 00:13:24.180
who was from the other clan

00:13:24.180 --> 00:13:26.180
one was Sa'd ibn Mu'adh

00:13:26.180 --> 00:13:27.180
who made the statement

00:13:27.180 --> 00:13:28.180
Sa'd ibn Ubada radiallahu anhu said no

00:13:28.180 --> 00:13:30.180
you won't kill him

00:13:30.180 --> 00:13:31.180
if he is from our clan

00:13:31.180 --> 00:13:32.180
you won't kill him

00:13:32.180 --> 00:13:33.180
how can you say

00:13:33.180 --> 00:13:35.180
that you will sort him out and so on

00:13:35.180 --> 00:13:36.180
and it pursued

00:13:36.180 --> 00:13:39.180
Usaid ibn Hudayr radiallahu anhu got up

00:13:39.180 --> 00:13:40.180
and he also added something

00:13:40.180 --> 00:13:41.180
he said no

00:13:41.180 --> 00:13:43.180
if this person has harmed the messenger

00:13:43.180 --> 00:13:44.180
then they deserve to be dealt with

00:13:44.180 --> 00:13:47.180
how dare someone say something of this nature

00:13:47.180 --> 00:13:48.180
and the Prophet sallallahu alaihi wasallam

00:13:48.180 --> 00:13:50.180
was standing and watching the Ansar

00:13:50.180 --> 00:13:51.180
talking amongst themselves

00:13:51.180 --> 00:13:53.180
with the Muhajireen and so on

00:13:53.180 --> 00:13:55.180
and there was this discussion

00:13:55.180 --> 00:13:56.180
and in Madina Munawwara

00:13:56.180 --> 00:13:59.180
people were all just

00:13:59.180 --> 00:14:01.180
into all these categories

00:14:01.180 --> 00:14:02.180
one group talking

00:14:02.180 --> 00:14:04.180
one group excited in the background

00:14:04.180 --> 00:14:06.180
really watching in glee

00:14:06.180 --> 00:14:07.180
as everything is happening

00:14:07.180 --> 00:14:08.180
according to their plan

00:14:08.180 --> 00:14:10.180
those were the hypocrites

00:14:10.180 --> 00:14:11.180
and one group saying

00:14:11.180 --> 00:14:13.180
this is a total fabrication

00:14:13.180 --> 00:14:16.180
so then the Prophet sallallahu alaihi wasallam

00:14:16.180 --> 00:14:19.180
goes into the room of Aisha radiallahu anhu

00:14:19.180 --> 00:14:21.180
and he greets

00:14:21.180 --> 00:14:23.180
now when he greets

00:14:23.180 --> 00:14:25.180
she thought some goodness is coming

00:14:25.180 --> 00:14:27.180
but instead of that

00:14:27.180 --> 00:14:28.180
he says

00:14:28.180 --> 00:14:29.180
tashahud

00:14:29.180 --> 00:14:31.180
ashadu alla ilaha illallah

00:14:31.180 --> 00:14:34.180
wa ashadu anna muhammadan abduhu wa rasuluhu

00:14:34.180 --> 00:14:35.180
then he says amma ba'du

00:14:35.180 --> 00:14:36.180
thereafter

00:14:36.180 --> 00:14:38.180
so now he is making a statement

00:14:38.180 --> 00:14:40.180
it's a statement regarding what happened

00:14:40.180 --> 00:14:41.180
he's saying

00:14:41.180 --> 00:14:42.180
oh Aisha

00:14:42.180 --> 00:14:44.180
if you are innocent

00:14:44.180 --> 00:14:46.180
Allah will reveal your innocence

00:14:46.180 --> 00:14:48.180
and if you have committed a sin

00:14:48.180 --> 00:14:49.180
remember

00:14:49.180 --> 00:14:51.180
you admit your error to Allah

00:14:51.180 --> 00:14:52.180
Allah will forgive you

00:14:52.180 --> 00:14:54.180
and Allah will cleanse you

00:14:54.180 --> 00:14:55.180
and so on

00:14:55.180 --> 00:14:56.180
so he gave her the options

00:14:56.180 --> 00:14:58.180
and she began to weep

00:14:58.180 --> 00:14:59.180
because this meant

00:14:59.180 --> 00:15:01.180
that there is still no clarification

00:15:01.180 --> 00:15:02.180
she began to weep

00:15:02.180 --> 00:15:05.180
until there came a time when she said

00:15:05.180 --> 00:15:07.180
if I am to say

00:15:07.180 --> 00:15:08.180
I am innocent

00:15:08.180 --> 00:15:10.180
they won't believe me

00:15:10.180 --> 00:15:12.180
and if I am to say

00:15:12.180 --> 00:15:13.180
that I am guilty

00:15:13.180 --> 00:15:14.180
that's what they want to hear

00:15:14.180 --> 00:15:15.180
but that would be a lie

00:15:15.180 --> 00:15:16.180
because I am innocent

00:15:16.180 --> 00:15:19.180
so I am in a fix basically

00:15:19.180 --> 00:15:20.180
caught between the two

00:15:20.180 --> 00:15:22.180
Aisha radiallahu anhu is saying

00:15:22.180 --> 00:15:23.180
and she says

00:15:23.180 --> 00:15:24.180
I told them

00:15:24.180 --> 00:15:26.180
that I cannot utter any words

00:15:26.180 --> 00:15:29.180
besides the words of the Prophet Yaqoob

00:15:29.180 --> 00:15:31.180
Jacob may peace be upon him

00:15:31.180 --> 00:15:34.180
when he had lost his son Yusuf alayhi salam

00:15:34.180 --> 00:15:35.180
he said

00:15:45.180 --> 00:15:47.180
my patience shall be beautiful

00:15:47.180 --> 00:15:48.180
by the help of Allah

00:15:48.180 --> 00:15:49.180
subhanahu wa ta'ala

00:15:49.180 --> 00:15:51.180
indeed Allah is the one

00:15:51.180 --> 00:15:53.180
Allah is the one who will assist

00:15:53.180 --> 00:15:54.180
regarding their statements

00:15:54.180 --> 00:15:56.180
and what they are describing

00:15:56.180 --> 00:15:57.180
this was the statement

00:15:57.180 --> 00:15:58.180
she repeated this

00:15:58.180 --> 00:15:59.180
and then she says

00:15:59.180 --> 00:16:03.180
as they walked out of the house

00:16:03.180 --> 00:16:05.180
before they could leave the house

00:16:05.180 --> 00:16:08.180
revelation came to Muhammad salallahu alayhi wasalam

00:16:08.180 --> 00:16:11.180
this was almost a month

00:16:11.180 --> 00:16:13.180
over a month later

00:16:21.180 --> 00:16:40.180
Arabic

00:16:40.180 --> 00:16:42.180
Allahu Akbar

00:16:42.180 --> 00:16:44.180
Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala says

00:16:44.180 --> 00:16:46.180
indeed those who have come

00:16:46.180 --> 00:16:48.180
with the fabrication

00:16:48.180 --> 00:16:51.180
are a group from amongst you

00:16:51.180 --> 00:16:53.180
imagine when revelation came out

00:16:53.180 --> 00:16:55.180
the word fabrication was used

00:16:55.180 --> 00:16:57.180
as soon as that word was used

00:16:57.180 --> 00:16:59.180
it was a clarification for everything

00:16:59.180 --> 00:17:02.180
because that's what they were waiting for

00:17:02.180 --> 00:17:04.180
the minute the term if was used

00:17:04.180 --> 00:17:06.180
it means a fabrication

00:17:06.180 --> 00:17:08.180
someone who has accused another person

00:17:08.180 --> 00:17:10.180
falsely of immorality

00:17:10.180 --> 00:17:12.180
so when Allah revealed the verses

00:17:12.180 --> 00:17:15.180
that those who have brought about

00:17:15.180 --> 00:17:16.180
this false accusation

00:17:16.180 --> 00:17:18.180
are a group from amongst you

00:17:18.180 --> 00:17:20.180
they knew it was already a lie

00:17:20.180 --> 00:17:21.180
Subhanallah

00:17:21.180 --> 00:17:22.180
then Allah says

00:17:22.180 --> 00:17:25.180
do not think that it is bad for you

00:17:25.180 --> 00:17:27.180
it is in fact good for you

00:17:27.180 --> 00:17:28.180
let's stop there for a moment

00:17:28.180 --> 00:17:30.180
today when people spread rumor about us

00:17:30.180 --> 00:17:32.180
do you know that sometimes

00:17:32.180 --> 00:17:35.180
your success is directly connected

00:17:35.180 --> 00:17:37.180
to the rumor that people spread about you

00:17:37.180 --> 00:17:39.180
as a direct result of it

00:17:39.180 --> 00:17:40.180
Allah gives you success

00:17:40.180 --> 00:17:42.180
in different aspects of your life

00:17:42.180 --> 00:17:44.180
because when they spread rumor

00:17:44.180 --> 00:17:46.180
they are taking away your sin

00:17:46.180 --> 00:17:48.180
when they've taken away your sins

00:17:48.180 --> 00:17:50.180
sometimes things you haven't even done

00:17:50.180 --> 00:17:52.180
because the rumor continues and spreads

00:17:52.180 --> 00:17:53.180
amongst a thousand people

00:17:53.180 --> 00:17:55.180
when you are only one man or one woman

00:17:55.180 --> 00:17:58.180
so a thousand people have taken away

00:17:58.180 --> 00:18:00.180
more than the sins you actually have

00:18:00.180 --> 00:18:03.180
by then giving you the good deeds they have

00:18:03.180 --> 00:18:04.180
what happens to you

00:18:04.180 --> 00:18:05.180
you become pure

00:18:05.180 --> 00:18:06.180
you become cleansed

00:18:06.180 --> 00:18:08.180
you become a person who's elevated

00:18:08.180 --> 00:18:10.180
your doors open one after the other

00:18:10.180 --> 00:18:11.180
you don't know

00:18:11.180 --> 00:18:13.180
how come I am leading such a happy life

00:18:13.180 --> 00:18:15.180
but it is all connected to the rumor

00:18:15.180 --> 00:18:16.180
that is spread against you

00:18:16.180 --> 00:18:18.180
Allah says don't ever think it's bad for you

00:18:18.180 --> 00:18:20.180
it's actually very good for you

00:18:20.180 --> 00:18:21.180
Subhanallah

00:18:21.180 --> 00:18:23.180
and then Allah says

00:18:23.180 --> 00:18:26.180
everyone who took part in that particular

00:18:26.180 --> 00:18:29.180
accusation shall bear their sin of it

00:18:29.180 --> 00:18:31.180
and the one who created the fabrication

00:18:31.180 --> 00:18:33.180
shall have a massive punishment

00:18:33.180 --> 00:18:36.180
who was Abdullah ibn Ubayy ibn Salul

00:18:36.180 --> 00:18:39.180
so Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala revealed these verses

00:18:39.180 --> 00:18:41.180
and Aisha radiallahu anha

00:18:41.180 --> 00:18:43.180
when she was told by Ummul Oman

00:18:43.180 --> 00:18:44.180
her mother

00:18:44.180 --> 00:18:45.180
get up

00:18:45.180 --> 00:18:46.180
why don't you embrace him

00:18:46.180 --> 00:18:48.180
because now the problem is sorted

00:18:48.180 --> 00:18:50.180
she says why should I get up and embrace him

00:18:50.180 --> 00:18:53.180
I have none to thank besides Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala

00:18:53.180 --> 00:18:56.180
she was obviously upset at the time

00:18:56.180 --> 00:18:58.180
because she was being accused

00:18:58.180 --> 00:18:59.180
and now she was so happy

00:18:59.180 --> 00:19:02.180
because the cleansing came from the heavens

00:19:02.180 --> 00:19:03.180
subhanallah

00:19:03.180 --> 00:19:05.180
and this is why she always used to say

00:19:05.180 --> 00:19:07.180
to her compatriots

00:19:07.180 --> 00:19:09.180
that you know I am the one

00:19:09.180 --> 00:19:11.180
whose name was cleansed from the heavens

00:19:11.180 --> 00:19:13.180
subhanallah

00:19:13.180 --> 00:19:14.180
and these were the verses

00:19:14.180 --> 00:19:15.180
Surah An-Nur

00:19:15.180 --> 00:19:16.180
if we pick up the Quran

00:19:16.180 --> 00:19:17.180
and read Surah An-Nur

00:19:17.180 --> 00:19:19.180
we will see these verses there

00:19:19.180 --> 00:19:20.180
beautiful powerful verses

00:19:20.180 --> 00:19:22.180
and this is why Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala

00:19:22.180 --> 00:19:23.180
describes this

00:19:23.180 --> 00:19:26.180
it is a very very interesting story

00:19:26.180 --> 00:19:28.180
but the lessons to be learned from there

00:19:28.180 --> 00:19:30.180
are even greater

00:19:30.180 --> 00:19:32.180
because Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala says

00:19:32.180 --> 00:19:46.180
...

00:19:46.180 --> 00:19:48.180
shouldn't the believers

00:19:48.180 --> 00:19:50.180
when they heard such a rumour

00:19:50.180 --> 00:19:52.180
think to themselves

00:19:52.180 --> 00:19:54.180
shouldn't they have thought to themselves

00:19:54.180 --> 00:19:56.180
that if we cannot do this

00:19:56.180 --> 00:19:58.180
she definitely cannot do it

00:19:58.180 --> 00:20:00.180
and this is what Abu Ayyub Al-Ansari

00:20:01.180 --> 00:20:02.180
had done

00:20:02.180 --> 00:20:03.180
and they should have said

00:20:03.180 --> 00:20:06.180
this is a fabrication and it's a lie

00:20:06.180 --> 00:20:19.180
...

00:20:19.180 --> 00:20:21.180
shouldn't you have uttered immediately

00:20:21.180 --> 00:20:22.180
as you heard it

00:20:22.180 --> 00:20:23.180
that look we should not be

00:20:23.180 --> 00:20:24.180
messing our tongues

00:20:24.180 --> 00:20:25.180
with this type of statement

00:20:25.180 --> 00:20:26.180
don't talk about this

00:20:26.180 --> 00:20:28.180
indeed it's a big fabrication

00:20:28.180 --> 00:20:29.180
against the pure people

00:20:29.180 --> 00:20:30.180
...

00:20:30.180 --> 00:20:32.180
so this is Allah teaching us

00:20:32.180 --> 00:20:33.180
when you hear rumour

00:20:33.180 --> 00:20:35.180
when you hear various comments

00:20:35.180 --> 00:20:37.180
the best thing is to say

00:20:37.180 --> 00:20:39.180
I don't want to mess my tongue

00:20:39.180 --> 00:20:40.180
with this statement

00:20:40.180 --> 00:20:41.180
and I don't want to utter that

00:20:41.180 --> 00:20:42.180
which is lies

00:20:42.180 --> 00:20:44.180
may Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala protect us

00:20:44.180 --> 00:20:45.180
then Allah says

00:20:45.180 --> 00:20:52.180
...

00:20:52.180 --> 00:20:53.180
let them bring forth

00:20:53.180 --> 00:20:56.180
four eye witnesses regarding the act

00:20:56.180 --> 00:20:57.180
if they don't bring those

00:20:57.180 --> 00:20:59.180
if they don't bring those four eye witnesses

00:20:59.180 --> 00:21:06.180
...

00:21:06.180 --> 00:21:07.180
then they are the liars

00:21:07.180 --> 00:21:09.180
in the eyes of Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala

00:21:09.180 --> 00:21:11.180
in fact at that point

00:21:11.180 --> 00:21:14.180
a punishment was sent by Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala

00:21:14.180 --> 00:21:16.180
for those who were spreading the accusation

00:21:16.180 --> 00:21:19.180
Allah says they had to be whipped

00:21:19.180 --> 00:21:20.180
eighty lashes

00:21:20.180 --> 00:21:22.180
may Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala protect us

00:21:22.180 --> 00:21:24.180
anyone who accuses

00:21:24.180 --> 00:21:26.180
a believing male or female

00:21:26.180 --> 00:21:28.180
of immorality and adultery

00:21:28.180 --> 00:21:31.180
they should be told to bring

00:21:31.180 --> 00:21:33.180
four eye witnesses

00:21:33.180 --> 00:21:35.180
who have witnessed the act

00:21:35.180 --> 00:21:36.180
if they cannot do that

00:21:36.180 --> 00:21:39.180
they should be lashed eighty lashes

00:21:39.180 --> 00:21:43.180
and this is the injunction of the Quran

00:21:43.180 --> 00:21:46.180
today we see people walking out there

00:21:46.180 --> 00:21:48.180
and we very very interestingly say

00:21:48.180 --> 00:21:49.180
you know what

00:21:49.180 --> 00:21:51.180
these people are having an affair

00:21:51.180 --> 00:21:52.180
or these people are going out

00:21:52.180 --> 00:21:53.180
wallahi

00:21:53.180 --> 00:21:55.180
you know what Allah says

00:21:55.180 --> 00:22:13.180
...

00:22:13.180 --> 00:22:16.560
you have received it with your tongues

00:22:16.560 --> 00:22:17.560
you have uttered it with your tongues

00:22:17.560 --> 00:22:20.560
you are saying the statement with your mouths

00:22:20.560 --> 00:22:22.560
and you are considering it light

00:22:22.560 --> 00:22:24.560
yet in the eyes of Allah

00:22:24.560 --> 00:22:27.560
it is a huge sin to accuse people

00:22:27.560 --> 00:22:30.560
may Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala protect us

00:22:30.560 --> 00:22:31.560
really

00:22:31.560 --> 00:22:32.560
look at the words

00:22:32.560 --> 00:22:33.560
then Allah says

00:22:33.560 --> 00:22:47.560
...

00:22:47.560 --> 00:22:49.560
those people who love to spread

00:22:49.560 --> 00:22:51.560
the tales of immorality

00:22:51.560 --> 00:22:53.560
amongst the believers

00:22:53.560 --> 00:22:56.560
for them there will be a severe punishment

00:22:56.560 --> 00:22:57.560
in this world

00:22:57.560 --> 00:22:59.560
and then in the next as well

00:22:59.560 --> 00:23:00.560
what does this mean

00:23:00.560 --> 00:23:02.560
people who like to spread stories

00:23:02.560 --> 00:23:03.560
true or false

00:23:03.560 --> 00:23:05.560
if it is a story of immorality

00:23:05.560 --> 00:23:06.560
why spread it

00:23:06.560 --> 00:23:08.560
you are encouraging others

00:23:08.560 --> 00:23:10.560
the first thing you are doing is

00:23:10.560 --> 00:23:11.560
you are backbiting

00:23:11.560 --> 00:23:12.560
if it is not backbiting

00:23:12.560 --> 00:23:13.560
it is slander

00:23:13.560 --> 00:23:14.560
and on top of that

00:23:14.560 --> 00:23:15.560
you will be telling others

00:23:15.560 --> 00:23:16.560
and people will start thinking

00:23:16.560 --> 00:23:18.560
well this is a sin that is common

00:23:18.560 --> 00:23:20.560
so if we are committing it

00:23:20.560 --> 00:23:22.560
then it doesn't make us any different

00:23:22.560 --> 00:23:23.560
and so on

00:23:23.560 --> 00:23:25.560
so it encourages people to actually sin

00:23:25.560 --> 00:23:26.560
Allah says that is why

00:23:26.560 --> 00:23:28.560
stories of immorality

00:23:28.560 --> 00:23:31.560
you should never ever spread them

00:23:31.560 --> 00:23:32.560
those who like to spread

00:23:32.560 --> 00:23:34.560
stories of immorality

00:23:34.560 --> 00:23:35.560
amongst the believing

00:23:35.560 --> 00:23:36.560
male and female

00:23:36.560 --> 00:23:37.560
they will be punished

00:23:37.560 --> 00:23:38.560
Allah says in this world

00:23:38.560 --> 00:23:39.560
and then the next

00:23:39.560 --> 00:23:41.560
may Allah safeguard us

00:23:41.560 --> 00:23:42.560
and from this the ulamas say

00:23:42.560 --> 00:23:44.560
that to read books

00:23:44.560 --> 00:23:47.560
that are what we would term

00:23:47.560 --> 00:23:49.560
x-rated full of stories of immorality

00:23:49.560 --> 00:23:50.560
is forbidden

00:23:50.560 --> 00:23:52.560
because it falls under this verse

00:23:52.560 --> 00:23:53.560
and the same applies

00:23:53.560 --> 00:23:55.560
pornography and so on

00:23:55.560 --> 00:23:56.560
and anything immoral

00:23:56.560 --> 00:23:57.560
even if there is a movie

00:23:57.560 --> 00:23:59.560
that has something immoral in it

00:23:59.560 --> 00:24:00.560
we should remember

00:24:00.560 --> 00:24:02.560
we should be further away from it

00:24:02.560 --> 00:24:04.560
may Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala protect us

00:24:04.560 --> 00:24:06.560
the reason why I say further away

00:24:06.560 --> 00:24:07.560
is we as muslimin

00:24:07.560 --> 00:24:09.560
shouldn't even be indulged

00:24:09.560 --> 00:24:11.560
in that in the first place

00:24:11.560 --> 00:24:13.560
may Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala protect us

00:24:13.560 --> 00:24:14.560
and grant us a lesson

00:24:14.560 --> 00:24:16.560
there are so many verses here

00:24:16.560 --> 00:24:18.560
that have a lesson for all of us

00:24:18.560 --> 00:24:20.560
now Aisha radi allahu anha

00:24:20.560 --> 00:24:21.560
her name was cleansed

00:24:21.560 --> 00:24:23.560
by Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala

00:24:23.560 --> 00:24:24.560
her status was elevated

00:24:24.560 --> 00:24:26.560
by Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala

00:24:26.560 --> 00:24:29.560
now abu bakr as-siddiq radi allahu anhu

00:24:29.560 --> 00:24:30.560
was faced with a difficulty

00:24:30.560 --> 00:24:32.560
what was the difficulty?

00:24:32.560 --> 00:24:33.560
that young man

00:24:33.560 --> 00:24:34.560
mistah ibn athatha

00:24:34.560 --> 00:24:36.560
who was spreading the rumour

00:24:36.560 --> 00:24:38.560
he was one of the relatives

00:24:38.560 --> 00:24:40.560
and abu bakr as-siddiq radi allahu anhu

00:24:40.560 --> 00:24:41.560
as we said

00:24:41.560 --> 00:24:42.560
used to spend on him

00:24:42.560 --> 00:24:43.560
and give him charities

00:24:43.560 --> 00:24:45.560
and look after him basically

00:24:45.560 --> 00:24:47.560
so when he spread the rumour

00:24:47.560 --> 00:24:49.560
abu bakr as-siddiq radi allahu anhu

00:24:49.560 --> 00:24:50.560
was so upset that he said

00:24:50.560 --> 00:24:52.560
wallahi i am not going to spend

00:24:52.560 --> 00:24:54.560
on this man again

00:24:54.560 --> 00:24:56.560
so Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala

00:24:56.560 --> 00:24:58.560
revealed verses after this

00:24:58.560 --> 00:25:00.560
to abu bakr as-siddiq

00:25:00.560 --> 00:25:02.560
or referring to abu bakr as-siddiq

00:25:02.560 --> 00:25:03.560
radi allahu anhu

00:25:03.560 --> 00:25:04.560
these verses revealed

00:25:04.560 --> 00:25:06.560
to rasulullah sallallahu alayhi wa sallam

00:25:06.560 --> 00:25:11.560
wa la ya'tali ulul fadli minkum wassati

00:25:11.560 --> 00:25:15.560
an yu'tu ulil qurba

00:25:15.560 --> 00:25:18.560
wal masakeen wal muhajireen

00:25:18.560 --> 00:25:20.560
fi sabeelillah

00:25:20.560 --> 00:25:23.560
wal ya'foo wal ya'sfahoo

00:25:23.560 --> 00:25:28.560
ala tuhibbon an yaghfir allahu lakum

00:25:28.560 --> 00:25:33.560
wallahu ghafoorun raheem

00:25:33.560 --> 00:25:36.560
those who have been granted virtue by Allah

00:25:36.560 --> 00:25:39.560
and ease and wealth by Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala

00:25:39.560 --> 00:25:42.560
they should never take an oath

00:25:42.560 --> 00:25:43.560
or make an oath

00:25:43.560 --> 00:25:46.560
that they are not going to spend upon the poor

00:25:46.560 --> 00:25:48.560
and upon people who have engaged in the hijra

00:25:48.560 --> 00:25:50.560
and upon those who are relatives

00:25:50.560 --> 00:25:52.560
they should not do that

00:25:52.560 --> 00:25:54.560
they should forgive and they should embrace

00:25:54.560 --> 00:25:58.560
for indeed do they not want to be forgiven by Allah

00:25:58.560 --> 00:25:59.560
the question is

00:25:59.560 --> 00:26:01.560
do you not want to be forgiven by Allah

00:26:01.560 --> 00:26:02.560
subhanahu wa ta'ala

00:26:02.560 --> 00:26:05.560
while Allah is most forgiving most merciful

00:26:05.560 --> 00:26:09.560
when Abu Bakr as-Siddiq radiallahu anhu heard this verse

00:26:09.560 --> 00:26:11.560
he immediately said yes indeed

00:26:11.560 --> 00:26:12.560
I want to be forgiven by Allah

00:26:12.560 --> 00:26:14.560
so I forgive this man

00:26:14.560 --> 00:26:15.560
what about the oath

00:26:15.560 --> 00:26:16.560
you had taken an oath

00:26:16.560 --> 00:26:19.560
well he had to pay the recompense of that oath

00:26:19.560 --> 00:26:21.560
in order to then break it

00:26:21.560 --> 00:26:24.560
so that he could fulfill the command of Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala

00:26:24.560 --> 00:26:26.560
and never again did he stop

00:26:26.560 --> 00:26:29.560
in his charitable deeds towards this particular man

00:26:29.560 --> 00:26:31.560
may Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala protect us

00:26:31.560 --> 00:26:34.560
today we would never help someone

00:26:34.560 --> 00:26:37.560
who has actively spread rumour about us

00:26:37.560 --> 00:26:39.560
and harmed us in our lives or our family members

00:26:39.560 --> 00:26:40.560
I don't think from amongst us

00:26:40.560 --> 00:26:42.560
there would be many if any

00:26:42.560 --> 00:26:44.560
who would actually do that

00:26:44.560 --> 00:26:47.560
and on top of that even if we were to help

00:26:47.560 --> 00:26:49.560
sometimes shaitan comes to us

00:26:49.560 --> 00:26:51.560
and makes us think right

00:26:51.560 --> 00:26:53.560
because I am financing this man

00:26:53.560 --> 00:26:54.560
I can now control him

00:26:54.560 --> 00:26:56.560
doesn't suddenly enslave the person

00:26:56.560 --> 00:26:58.560
may Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala protect us

00:26:58.560 --> 00:27:00.560
and may Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala make us

00:27:00.560 --> 00:27:01.560
from amongst those whom

00:27:01.560 --> 00:27:03.560
when we spend we spend for his cause

00:27:03.560 --> 00:27:05.560
and may he make us from those who learn a lesson

00:27:05.560 --> 00:27:08.560
from Abu Bakr al-Siddiq radiallahu anhu

00:27:08.560 --> 00:27:10.560
do you know why he forgave

00:27:10.560 --> 00:27:13.560
one of the reasons obviously was the instruction of Allah

00:27:13.560 --> 00:27:16.560
but he says I want to be forgiven by Allah

00:27:16.560 --> 00:27:18.560
so let me forgive this man

00:27:18.560 --> 00:27:20.560
if we forgive people Allah will forgive us

00:27:20.560 --> 00:27:22.560
irhamu man fil ardi

00:27:22.560 --> 00:27:24.560
yarhamkum man fil sama

00:27:24.560 --> 00:27:26.560
have mercy upon those on earth

00:27:26.560 --> 00:27:29.560
and Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala will have mercy upon you

00:27:29.560 --> 00:27:33.560
so if we have a quality of forgiving people

00:27:33.560 --> 00:27:35.560
you will find that Allah's quality of forgiveness

00:27:35.560 --> 00:27:37.560
is far greater than anything

00:27:37.560 --> 00:27:38.560
we can come up with

00:27:38.560 --> 00:27:39.560
and this is why

00:27:39.560 --> 00:27:41.560
find it in your heart to forgive

00:27:41.560 --> 00:27:43.560
for indeed when Allah sees that

00:27:43.560 --> 00:27:45.560
on the day that we need forgiveness

00:27:45.560 --> 00:27:47.560
we will find Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala

00:27:47.560 --> 00:27:48.560
forgiving us

00:27:48.560 --> 00:27:51.560
now this is a very very powerful verse

00:27:51.560 --> 00:27:55.560
and these entire verses that we have read today

00:27:55.560 --> 00:27:58.560
very powerful the lessons are all in surah al-nur

00:27:58.560 --> 00:28:00.560
if we turn the pages of surah al-nur

00:28:00.560 --> 00:28:02.560
we will come to learn

00:28:02.560 --> 00:28:04.560
whatever we have said this evening

00:28:04.560 --> 00:28:07.560
and alhamdulillah we ask Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala

00:28:07.560 --> 00:28:08.560
to grant us purity

00:28:08.560 --> 00:28:11.560
and to grant us chastity to protect us

00:28:11.560 --> 00:28:12.560
and our offspring

00:28:12.560 --> 00:28:14.560
our family members and the ummah at large

00:28:14.560 --> 00:28:17.560
from immoral behaviour

00:28:17.560 --> 00:28:20.560
may Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala purify us all

00:28:20.560 --> 00:28:22.560
now we have

00:28:22.560 --> 00:28:24.560
another battle that took place

00:28:24.560 --> 00:28:26.560
at the time of Rasulullah sallallahu alaihi wa sallam

00:28:26.560 --> 00:28:29.560
it is reported in the fifth year of Hijra

00:28:29.560 --> 00:28:31.560
and when in the fifth year

00:28:31.560 --> 00:28:33.560
the majority say in the month of Shawwal

00:28:33.560 --> 00:28:35.560
which was just after Ramadan

00:28:35.560 --> 00:28:37.560
you see yesterday we made mention of

00:28:37.560 --> 00:28:38.560
Banu al-Nadheer

00:28:38.560 --> 00:28:40.560
the tribe and the group of people

00:28:40.560 --> 00:28:42.560
who were told to leave

00:28:42.560 --> 00:28:44.560
Al Madinatul Munawwara

00:28:44.560 --> 00:28:47.560
and these people a lot of them went to

00:28:47.560 --> 00:28:50.560
a place near Sham known as Adra'at

00:28:50.560 --> 00:28:52.560
but there were some of them

00:28:52.560 --> 00:28:54.560
a group of them who had gone to Khaybar

00:28:54.560 --> 00:28:56.560
from amongst them was Huyay ibn al-Akhtab

00:28:56.560 --> 00:28:57.560
and a few others

00:28:57.560 --> 00:28:58.560
these were the senior people

00:28:58.560 --> 00:29:01.560
from those who were expelled from Banu al-Nadheer

00:29:01.560 --> 00:29:02.560
that was a Jewish clan

00:29:02.560 --> 00:29:04.560
in the outskirts of Madinatul Munawwara

00:29:04.560 --> 00:29:06.560
they had gone to Khaybar

00:29:06.560 --> 00:29:09.560
from Khaybar they decided

00:29:09.560 --> 00:29:10.560
we are wealthy

00:29:10.560 --> 00:29:12.560
we have a lot of date palms

00:29:12.560 --> 00:29:14.560
lot of dates and so on

00:29:14.560 --> 00:29:15.560
lot of produce

00:29:15.560 --> 00:29:17.560
why don't we form a little committee

00:29:17.560 --> 00:29:19.560
and we let this committee go

00:29:19.560 --> 00:29:21.560
and visit all the tribes and clans

00:29:21.560 --> 00:29:24.560
mainly the two major groups

00:29:24.560 --> 00:29:26.560
one was Ghatafan and one was Quraysh

00:29:26.560 --> 00:29:29.560
we will go to Ghatafan and speak to them

00:29:29.560 --> 00:29:31.560
and we will go to Quraysh and speak to them

00:29:31.560 --> 00:29:33.560
and we will bring them together

00:29:33.560 --> 00:29:35.560
and we will be allied together

00:29:35.560 --> 00:29:37.560
and as a confederate

00:29:37.560 --> 00:29:40.560
we will then march on to Madinatul Munawwara

00:29:40.560 --> 00:29:42.560
and wipe out the Muslims for once and for all

00:29:42.560 --> 00:29:46.560
because they chased us out of Al Madinatul Munawwara

00:29:46.560 --> 00:29:48.560
now to refresh your memories

00:29:48.560 --> 00:29:50.560
the reason why they were expelled

00:29:50.560 --> 00:29:52.560
was they broke the treaty

00:29:52.560 --> 00:29:54.560
they wanted to murder Muhammad SAW

00:29:54.560 --> 00:29:56.560
and they were caught red handed

00:29:56.560 --> 00:29:57.560
and on top of that

00:29:57.560 --> 00:30:00.560
they had broken the treaty in several other ways

00:30:00.560 --> 00:30:04.560
so Muhammad SAW asked them to leave

00:30:04.560 --> 00:30:07.560
and that was actually some point of mercy

00:30:07.560 --> 00:30:10.560
because they were guilty of war crimes

00:30:10.560 --> 00:30:12.560
they could have been executed rightfully

00:30:12.560 --> 00:30:13.560
but they were not

00:30:13.560 --> 00:30:14.560
they were asked to leave

00:30:14.560 --> 00:30:17.560
so these people they sent a team to Ghatafan

00:30:17.560 --> 00:30:18.560
they told Ghatafan

00:30:18.560 --> 00:30:22.560
look we want you to give us as many men as you can

00:30:22.560 --> 00:30:25.560
we're going to come together and make an alliance

00:30:25.560 --> 00:30:27.560
and we will pay you for it

00:30:27.560 --> 00:30:30.560
because Ghatafan they had no problem

00:30:30.560 --> 00:30:31.560
they had no problem at all

00:30:31.560 --> 00:30:32.560
they did not want to fight

00:30:32.560 --> 00:30:34.560
Quraysh was the one who wanted to fight

00:30:34.560 --> 00:30:37.560
so these people said okay we will pay you

00:30:37.560 --> 00:30:40.560
Ghatafan says how much are you going to pay us

00:30:40.560 --> 00:30:42.560
so the people of Khyber

00:30:42.560 --> 00:30:43.560
these people of Banu Nadir

00:30:43.560 --> 00:30:47.560
they said we will pay you one year

00:30:47.560 --> 00:30:51.560
produce of dates from the whole of Khyber

00:30:51.560 --> 00:30:52.560
now that's a lot

00:30:52.560 --> 00:30:55.560
it's like saying the economy of our whole country

00:30:55.560 --> 00:30:56.560
for one year will go to you

00:30:56.560 --> 00:30:58.560
may Allah protect us

00:30:58.560 --> 00:31:01.560
so these people agreed

00:31:01.560 --> 00:31:03.560
no problem we join your alliance

00:31:03.560 --> 00:31:06.560
in the meantime the same group went to Quraysh

00:31:06.560 --> 00:31:08.560
and they spoke to Abu Sufyan

00:31:08.560 --> 00:31:09.560
look we have the alliance

00:31:09.560 --> 00:31:12.560
it's already made up of little tribes and groups

00:31:12.560 --> 00:31:14.560
and Ghatafan has joined us with thousands of men

00:31:14.560 --> 00:31:16.560
you also bring men and so on

00:31:16.560 --> 00:31:20.560
and Quraysh they had a gripe against the Muslims

00:31:20.560 --> 00:31:22.560
they wanted to settle scores

00:31:22.560 --> 00:31:24.560
so they said this is a brilliant idea

00:31:24.560 --> 00:31:26.560
and in no time they agreed

00:31:26.560 --> 00:31:28.560
they decided we are going to join

00:31:28.560 --> 00:31:29.560
and thereafter they said

00:31:29.560 --> 00:31:31.560
let's march on to Madinah Monawara

00:31:31.560 --> 00:31:34.560
they gathered 10,000 men

00:31:34.560 --> 00:31:36.560
now in the meantime the Prophet sallallahu alaihi wasallam

00:31:36.560 --> 00:31:39.560
knew everything that was going on

00:31:39.560 --> 00:31:43.560
he was aware of what the people of Banu Nadir were doing

00:31:43.560 --> 00:31:45.560
he was aware of the agreement with Ghatafan

00:31:45.560 --> 00:31:47.560
he was aware of the agreement with Quraysh

00:31:47.560 --> 00:31:48.560
and he was also aware

00:31:48.560 --> 00:31:51.560
that now they want to march on to Madinah Monawara

00:31:51.560 --> 00:31:53.560
so the Prophet sallallahu alaihi wasallam

00:31:53.560 --> 00:31:55.560
got together his companions

00:31:55.560 --> 00:31:57.560
and he says oh my companions

00:31:57.560 --> 00:31:59.560
what should we do

00:31:59.560 --> 00:32:01.560
10,000 strong men

00:32:01.560 --> 00:32:04.560
heavily armed from different tribes and groups

00:32:04.560 --> 00:32:06.560
and alliance Al Ahzab

00:32:06.560 --> 00:32:08.560
they are coming towards Madinah Monawara

00:32:08.560 --> 00:32:09.560
what should we do

00:32:09.560 --> 00:32:12.560
so the different companions began to make suggestions

00:32:12.560 --> 00:32:14.560
until Salman Al Farsi

00:32:14.560 --> 00:32:15.560
the man from Persia

00:32:15.560 --> 00:32:18.560
the man whom we spoke about

00:32:18.560 --> 00:32:20.560
how he accepted Islam

00:32:20.560 --> 00:32:22.560
and his father

00:32:22.560 --> 00:32:25.560
was one of the fire worshippers in Persia

00:32:25.560 --> 00:32:27.560
and he had then left

00:32:27.560 --> 00:32:28.560
and gone to Assham

00:32:28.560 --> 00:32:30.560
where he became a Christian

00:32:30.560 --> 00:32:32.560
and from there he was enslaved

00:32:32.560 --> 00:32:34.560
on his way to Arabia

00:32:34.560 --> 00:32:36.560
in pursuit of the messenger

00:32:36.560 --> 00:32:38.560
and when he came to Madinah Monawara

00:32:38.560 --> 00:32:40.560
how he accepted Islam

00:32:40.560 --> 00:32:42.560
and how the Prophet sallallahu alaihi wasallam

00:32:42.560 --> 00:32:44.560
assisted him to pay

00:32:44.560 --> 00:32:46.560
those who had enslaved him

00:32:46.560 --> 00:32:48.560
in order for him to buy his freedom

00:32:48.560 --> 00:32:50.560
by planting those date palms

00:32:50.560 --> 00:32:52.560
and we said from 300 of them

00:32:52.560 --> 00:32:54.560
none of those date palms had actually died

00:32:54.560 --> 00:32:56.560
this is the same man

00:32:56.560 --> 00:32:57.560
he says oh messenger

00:32:57.560 --> 00:32:59.560
in my area

00:32:59.560 --> 00:33:01.560
which means in Persia

00:33:01.560 --> 00:33:03.560
when there is a big army that is coming

00:33:03.560 --> 00:33:05.560
and we want to block the horses from entering

00:33:05.560 --> 00:33:07.560
we create, we dig a trench

00:33:07.560 --> 00:33:09.560
around the city

00:33:09.560 --> 00:33:11.560
we dig a trench around the city

00:33:11.560 --> 00:33:13.560
now for us to think of a trench

00:33:13.560 --> 00:33:15.560
around the whole of Madinah

00:33:15.560 --> 00:33:17.560
that is something very difficult

00:33:17.560 --> 00:33:19.560
but for your information

00:33:19.560 --> 00:33:21.560
there was no need to dig the trench

00:33:21.560 --> 00:33:23.560
around the whole of Madinah

00:33:23.560 --> 00:33:25.560
because there were only certain places

00:33:25.560 --> 00:33:27.560
from which the army could have entered Madinah

00:33:27.560 --> 00:33:29.560
on some parts it was very rocky

00:33:29.560 --> 00:33:31.560
some parts it was mountainous

00:33:31.560 --> 00:33:33.560
they couldn't enter from those parts

00:33:33.560 --> 00:33:35.560
only the flat land

00:33:35.560 --> 00:33:37.560
where they could have come from

00:33:37.560 --> 00:33:39.560
that is where the trench was then agreed to be dug

00:33:39.560 --> 00:33:41.560
but the Prophet ﷺ asked his companions

00:33:41.560 --> 00:33:43.560
what do you all think of this?

00:33:43.560 --> 00:33:45.560
some new strategy of war

00:33:45.560 --> 00:33:47.560
nobody had known about it before

00:33:47.560 --> 00:33:49.560
the people here

00:33:49.560 --> 00:33:51.560
no one was aware that this was going to happen

00:33:51.560 --> 00:33:53.560
so the Prophet ﷺ

00:33:53.560 --> 00:33:55.560
after having consulted his companions

00:33:55.560 --> 00:33:57.560
agreed and they went out on horseback

00:33:57.560 --> 00:33:59.560
to look where should this thing be dug

00:33:59.560 --> 00:34:01.560
they demarcated it correctly

00:34:01.560 --> 00:34:03.560
and every 40 feet

00:34:03.560 --> 00:34:05.560
was given to 10 companions to dig

00:34:05.560 --> 00:34:07.560
and the Prophet ﷺ

00:34:07.560 --> 00:34:09.560
himself joined in

00:34:09.560 --> 00:34:11.560
also in one of the groups

00:34:11.560 --> 00:34:13.560
ﷺ

00:34:13.560 --> 00:34:15.560
not like the leaders of today

00:34:15.560 --> 00:34:17.560
they sit back and the army is busy working

00:34:17.560 --> 00:34:19.560
here the messenger ﷺ

00:34:19.560 --> 00:34:21.560
so much so that was a time of hunger

00:34:21.560 --> 00:34:23.560
it was a time when they had a few days

00:34:23.560 --> 00:34:25.560
to achieve this whole

00:34:25.560 --> 00:34:27.560
huge achievement

00:34:27.560 --> 00:34:29.560
to dig this big trench

00:34:29.560 --> 00:34:31.560
they just had a few days

00:34:31.560 --> 00:34:33.560
it is reported that in total

00:34:33.560 --> 00:34:35.560
this trench was 10 kilometers long

00:34:35.560 --> 00:34:37.560
in the different parts of it

00:34:37.560 --> 00:34:39.560
22 feet wide

00:34:39.560 --> 00:34:41.560
16 feet deep

00:34:41.560 --> 00:34:43.560
took 6 days to dig

00:34:43.560 --> 00:34:45.560
and each 10 companions

00:34:45.560 --> 00:34:47.560
were handed 40 feet to dig

00:34:47.560 --> 00:34:49.560
Subhanallah

00:34:49.560 --> 00:34:51.560
imagine this is quite deep

00:34:51.560 --> 00:34:53.560
it's not a joke and it's quite wide as well

00:34:53.560 --> 00:34:55.560
because a horse

00:34:55.560 --> 00:34:57.560
as the horses are coming

00:34:57.560 --> 00:34:59.560
they don't go so deep

00:34:59.560 --> 00:35:01.560
they would refuse to get in

00:35:01.560 --> 00:35:03.560
and what would happen is

00:35:03.560 --> 00:35:05.560
an opportunity to be with all their

00:35:05.560 --> 00:35:07.560
arrows and spears

00:35:07.560 --> 00:35:09.560
and weaponry on the

00:35:09.560 --> 00:35:11.560
sides such that if anyone

00:35:11.560 --> 00:35:13.560
attempted to come they would be

00:35:13.560 --> 00:35:15.560
pelted or they would be immediately

00:35:15.560 --> 00:35:17.560
attacked with arrows

00:35:17.560 --> 00:35:19.560
and so on

00:35:19.560 --> 00:35:21.560
so this was something in no

00:35:21.560 --> 00:35:23.560
time Subhanallah

00:35:23.560 --> 00:35:25.560
this was done we said it took them

00:35:25.560 --> 00:35:27.560
6 days these 6 days

00:35:27.560 --> 00:35:29.560
were 6 days of great difficulty

00:35:29.560 --> 00:35:31.560
where they were working

00:35:31.560 --> 00:35:33.560
flat out Subhanallah

00:35:33.560 --> 00:35:35.560
because they had to do it urgently

00:35:35.560 --> 00:35:37.560
and in these 6 days it's important for me

00:35:37.560 --> 00:35:39.560
to make mention of some of the miracles

00:35:39.560 --> 00:35:41.560
of Rasulullah Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam

00:35:41.560 --> 00:35:43.560
he was digging himself

00:35:43.560 --> 00:35:45.560
and when they had

00:35:45.560 --> 00:35:47.560
a huge rock to break

00:35:47.560 --> 00:35:49.560
and they couldn't break it they called him

00:35:49.560 --> 00:35:51.560
Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam

00:35:51.560 --> 00:35:53.560
according to some narrations he was given

00:35:53.560 --> 00:35:55.560
the power of 30 men Subhanallah

00:35:55.560 --> 00:35:57.560
he was given the power of 30

00:35:57.560 --> 00:35:59.560
men Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam

00:35:59.560 --> 00:36:01.560
and he would then

00:36:01.560 --> 00:36:03.560
destroy the rock

00:36:03.560 --> 00:36:05.560
and flatten it out or

00:36:05.560 --> 00:36:07.560
make it rubble Sallallahu

00:36:07.560 --> 00:36:09.560
Alaihi Wasallam yet the companions were

00:36:09.560 --> 00:36:11.560
unable to do that so Jabir Ibn

00:36:11.560 --> 00:36:13.560
Abdullah Radhiallahu Anhu says when he lifted

00:36:13.560 --> 00:36:15.560
a rock in order to hit it on another one

00:36:15.560 --> 00:36:17.560
I saw that he had tied a

00:36:17.560 --> 00:36:19.560
rock on his belly because of hunger

00:36:19.560 --> 00:36:21.560
Subhanallah Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam

00:36:21.560 --> 00:36:23.560
so a person is hungry

00:36:23.560 --> 00:36:25.560
try it out it actually works

00:36:25.560 --> 00:36:27.560
I was speaking to someone from Europe

00:36:27.560 --> 00:36:29.560
complaining about how long the fast is

00:36:29.560 --> 00:36:31.560
I said have you ever tried the Sunnah

00:36:31.560 --> 00:36:33.560
you know tie a rock they started laughing

00:36:33.560 --> 00:36:35.560
I said you know what if you can't tie

00:36:35.560 --> 00:36:37.560
a hot water bottle or a cold water bottle

00:36:37.560 --> 00:36:39.560
it might work may Allah Subhanahu

00:36:39.560 --> 00:36:41.560
Alaihi Wasallam protect us what it does

00:36:41.560 --> 00:36:43.560
it actually flattens the belly and

00:36:43.560 --> 00:36:45.560
pushes it in so that you don't feel

00:36:45.560 --> 00:36:47.560
hungry although you are very hungry

00:36:47.560 --> 00:36:49.560
Subhanallah

00:36:49.560 --> 00:36:51.560
so Rasulullah Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam

00:36:51.560 --> 00:36:53.560
when Jabir Ibn Abdullah saw this

00:36:53.560 --> 00:36:55.560
he felt that this is the messenger

00:36:55.560 --> 00:36:57.560
he is working so hard

00:36:57.560 --> 00:36:59.560
he saw all this dust

00:36:59.560 --> 00:37:01.560
on the messenger Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam's body

00:37:01.560 --> 00:37:03.560
and he saw a rock tied on his belly

00:37:03.560 --> 00:37:05.560
and he then went home

00:37:05.560 --> 00:37:07.560
he tells his wife home was very close

00:37:07.560 --> 00:37:09.560
not very far from the trench he says

00:37:09.560 --> 00:37:11.560
what do we have she says well we have a goat

00:37:11.560 --> 00:37:13.560
and we have a little bit of barley

00:37:13.560 --> 00:37:15.560
so or wheat and

00:37:15.560 --> 00:37:17.560
he says okay let me slaughter

00:37:17.560 --> 00:37:19.560
this thing and prepare a good meal put this thing

00:37:19.560 --> 00:37:21.560
in the oven and I'm calling Nabi Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam

00:37:21.560 --> 00:37:23.560
with one or two men so the Prophet

00:37:23.560 --> 00:37:25.560
Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam then was told by

00:37:25.560 --> 00:37:27.560
Jabir Ibn Abdullah that

00:37:27.560 --> 00:37:29.560
Ya Rasulallah Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam

00:37:29.560 --> 00:37:31.560
if you can come to

00:37:31.560 --> 00:37:33.560
my home I've prepared a small

00:37:33.560 --> 00:37:35.560
meal you and perhaps you can bring one or

00:37:35.560 --> 00:37:37.560
two people

00:37:37.560 --> 00:37:39.560
so the Prophet Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam asked him

00:37:39.560 --> 00:37:41.560
what he said he repeated it

00:37:41.560 --> 00:37:43.560
when he said that the Prophet Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam

00:37:43.560 --> 00:37:45.560
made an announcement loud

00:37:45.560 --> 00:37:47.560
announcement he says we have

00:37:47.560 --> 00:37:49.560
been invited to the house of Jabir

00:37:49.560 --> 00:37:51.560
Ibn Abdullah let's all go for a meal

00:37:51.560 --> 00:37:53.560
now he was shocked how are we going to go

00:37:53.560 --> 00:37:55.560
Rasulullah Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam

00:37:55.560 --> 00:37:57.560
I only had told him

00:37:57.560 --> 00:37:59.560
to bring along one or two people because

00:37:59.560 --> 00:38:01.560
how are we going to feed the whole army here

00:38:01.560 --> 00:38:03.560
and a lot of the companions

00:38:03.560 --> 00:38:05.560
had come and Jabir Ibn Abdullah

00:38:05.560 --> 00:38:07.560
tells his wife that you know what

00:38:07.560 --> 00:38:09.560
they are coming and there's a lot of them

00:38:09.560 --> 00:38:11.560
now think what would happen in our case

00:38:11.560 --> 00:38:13.560
I think we would be dead meat

00:38:13.560 --> 00:38:15.560
may Allah Subhanahu Wa Ta'ala protect us

00:38:15.560 --> 00:38:17.560
in some cases and in some

00:38:17.560 --> 00:38:19.560
cases they would be very happy Masha Allah

00:38:19.560 --> 00:38:21.560
you say no problem I know of some

00:38:21.560 --> 00:38:23.560
cases where they say you can bring as many as you want

00:38:23.560 --> 00:38:25.560
but Mochachos is round the corner you better

00:38:25.560 --> 00:38:27.560
bring some food there as well Masha Allah

00:38:27.560 --> 00:38:29.560
Allah Subhanahu Wa Ta'ala grant us ease

00:38:29.560 --> 00:38:31.560
and Baraka Wallahi we have so much

00:38:31.560 --> 00:38:33.560
convenience Allah has made life so easy

00:38:33.560 --> 00:38:35.560
for us still sometimes we

00:38:35.560 --> 00:38:37.560
are not hospitable Masha Allah

00:38:37.560 --> 00:38:39.560
I know this community full of hospitality

00:38:39.560 --> 00:38:41.560
sometimes you find Shaytan

00:38:41.560 --> 00:38:43.560
overtakes us and we feel lazy

00:38:43.560 --> 00:38:45.560
when the Baraka is in feeding the guest

00:38:45.560 --> 00:38:47.560
sometimes the Baraka is

00:38:47.560 --> 00:38:49.560
feeding the guest the Sahaba

00:38:49.560 --> 00:38:51.560
used to get worried when no guest

00:38:51.560 --> 00:38:53.560
used to come to their homes they used to think

00:38:53.560 --> 00:38:55.560
what's going on is there something wrong with my wealth

00:38:55.560 --> 00:38:57.560
is there something wrong with my sustenance

00:38:57.560 --> 00:38:59.560
no Baraka in the home so what

00:38:59.560 --> 00:39:01.560
happened here when Rasulullah

00:39:01.560 --> 00:39:03.560
Sallallahu Alayhi Wasallam was coming

00:39:03.560 --> 00:39:05.560
with all his companions Jabir

00:39:05.560 --> 00:39:07.560
tells his wife and now there are

00:39:07.560 --> 00:39:09.560
a few narrations I'm mentioning one of them

00:39:09.560 --> 00:39:11.560
in one narration the wife says

00:39:11.560 --> 00:39:13.560
does the Prophet Sallallahu Alayhi Wasallam

00:39:13.560 --> 00:39:15.560
know that we had only told

00:39:15.560 --> 00:39:17.560
him one or two people and

00:39:17.560 --> 00:39:19.560
he says yes well in that

00:39:19.560 --> 00:39:21.560
case no problem in that case

00:39:21.560 --> 00:39:23.560
it's fine Subhanallah when the

00:39:23.560 --> 00:39:25.560
Prophet Sallallahu Alayhi Wasallam was coming he sent

00:39:25.560 --> 00:39:27.560
an instruction go and tell your family

00:39:27.560 --> 00:39:29.560
that they should not take the

00:39:29.560 --> 00:39:31.560
pot off the fire and they should

00:39:31.560 --> 00:39:33.560
not remove whatever is in the oven

00:39:33.560 --> 00:39:35.560
from it Subhanallah

00:39:35.560 --> 00:39:37.560
they were about to witness

00:39:37.560 --> 00:39:39.560
a miracle the Prophet Sallallahu

00:39:39.560 --> 00:39:41.560
Alayhi Wasallam came he removed

00:39:41.560 --> 00:39:43.560
from the pot and he kept on removing

00:39:43.560 --> 00:39:45.560
from the pot and he kept on removing

00:39:45.560 --> 00:39:47.560
from the pot and he kept on removing

00:39:47.560 --> 00:39:49.560
from the oven until the whole army

00:39:49.560 --> 00:39:51.560
was fed Subhanallah

00:39:51.560 --> 00:39:53.560
this was the miracle similar

00:39:53.560 --> 00:39:55.560
miracle had happened to the Prophet

00:39:55.560 --> 00:39:57.560
Isa Alayhi Wasallam a four time

00:39:57.560 --> 00:39:59.560
Jesus may peace be upon him

00:39:59.560 --> 00:40:01.560
we have made mention

00:40:01.560 --> 00:40:03.560
of this in the past and it is

00:40:03.560 --> 00:40:05.560
made mention of even in the Ahadeel

00:40:05.560 --> 00:40:07.560
and the records of the Muslimin

00:40:07.560 --> 00:40:09.560
that this is from amongst the miracles

00:40:09.560 --> 00:40:11.560
of the Prophet Jesus may peace be upon

00:40:11.560 --> 00:40:13.560
him Isa Alayhi Wasallam

00:40:13.560 --> 00:40:15.560
here it has repeated itself

00:40:15.560 --> 00:40:17.560
with Muhammad Sallallahu Alayhi Wasallam

00:40:17.560 --> 00:40:19.560
and we ask

00:40:19.560 --> 00:40:21.560
Allah Subhanahu Wa Ta'ala to grant us goodness

00:40:21.560 --> 00:40:23.560
they were shocked they were not only

00:40:23.560 --> 00:40:25.560
shocked but it resulted

00:40:25.560 --> 00:40:27.560
in them being reinforced their

00:40:27.560 --> 00:40:29.560
Iman being strengthened they

00:40:29.560 --> 00:40:31.560
went back to dig and Subhanallah

00:40:31.560 --> 00:40:33.560
in no time this army had

00:40:33.560 --> 00:40:35.560
arrived when the army

00:40:35.560 --> 00:40:37.560
came they were also surprised

00:40:37.560 --> 00:40:39.560
they had heard that the Muslims

00:40:39.560 --> 00:40:41.560
are doing something strange

00:40:41.560 --> 00:40:43.560
because there was

00:40:43.560 --> 00:40:45.560
one more tribe of these people

00:40:45.560 --> 00:40:47.560
of the book on the outskirts of

00:40:47.560 --> 00:40:49.560
Medina known as Banu Quraidha

00:40:49.560 --> 00:40:51.560
we heard that Banu Qinuqa' was expelled

00:40:51.560 --> 00:40:53.560
Banu An-Nadir were expelled

00:40:53.560 --> 00:40:55.560
and as for Banu Quraidha

00:40:55.560 --> 00:40:57.560
they were there but they felt this time

00:40:57.560 --> 00:40:59.560
there is no ways the Muslims are going to

00:40:59.560 --> 00:41:01.560
win they're going to be wiped out so they

00:41:01.560 --> 00:41:03.560
align themselves

00:41:03.560 --> 00:41:05.560
with the Confederates

00:41:05.560 --> 00:41:07.560
they even sent or they were trying

00:41:07.560 --> 00:41:09.560
to send some camels with some dates

00:41:09.560 --> 00:41:11.560
and some food and assistance

00:41:11.560 --> 00:41:13.560
which was intercepted by the Muslims

00:41:13.560 --> 00:41:15.560
and it was taken away and the Prophet

00:41:15.560 --> 00:41:17.560
Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam then made it clear

00:41:17.560 --> 00:41:19.560
that these people have broken the treaty as well

00:41:19.560 --> 00:41:21.560
Banu Quraidha and Banu

00:41:21.560 --> 00:41:23.560
Quraidha they had a plan they had

00:41:23.560 --> 00:41:25.560
hatched a plan Insha'Allah we will see it in a few moments

00:41:25.560 --> 00:41:27.560
so the armies

00:41:27.560 --> 00:41:29.560
came they were shocked they looked at this

00:41:29.560 --> 00:41:31.560
trench they couldn't move as they tried

00:41:31.560 --> 00:41:33.560
they were being attacked by spears

00:41:33.560 --> 00:41:35.560
Muslims so they couldn't move they were

00:41:35.560 --> 00:41:37.560
camping outside if they went around

00:41:37.560 --> 00:41:39.560
the Prophet Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam had spread

00:41:39.560 --> 00:41:41.560
his army out all the Muslims were there

00:41:41.560 --> 00:41:43.560
because they were in Medina so there was

00:41:43.560 --> 00:41:45.560
no question of how many men were the Muslims

00:41:45.560 --> 00:41:47.560
they were all there and

00:41:47.560 --> 00:41:49.560
so there were some on the mountains

00:41:49.560 --> 00:41:51.560
taking care of that some on the rocky land

00:41:51.560 --> 00:41:53.560
taking care of that some on the different

00:41:53.560 --> 00:41:55.560
parts of Medina taking care of that

00:41:55.560 --> 00:41:57.560
and the strategic trench

00:41:57.560 --> 00:41:59.560
which was dug Subhanallah

00:41:59.560 --> 00:42:01.560
was heavily protected by the

00:42:01.560 --> 00:42:03.560
Muslims which means nobody can

00:42:03.560 --> 00:42:05.560
come in

00:42:05.560 --> 00:42:07.560
tried to come in he was immediately attacked

00:42:07.560 --> 00:42:09.560
in fact there was another man

00:42:09.560 --> 00:42:11.560
who tried to come in as well

00:42:11.560 --> 00:42:13.560
and he was also attacked but before we

00:42:13.560 --> 00:42:15.560
get to that in the meantime in

00:42:15.560 --> 00:42:17.560
Medina Munawwara

00:42:17.560 --> 00:42:19.560
something happened Banu Quraidha

00:42:19.560 --> 00:42:21.560
decided you know what

00:42:21.560 --> 00:42:23.560
we need to see how best

00:42:23.560 --> 00:42:25.560
we can attack the Muslims from behind

00:42:25.560 --> 00:42:27.560
so let us first go

00:42:27.560 --> 00:42:29.560
and try and cause

00:42:29.560 --> 00:42:31.560
disturbance amongst their women and children

00:42:31.560 --> 00:42:33.560
who are left in the city

00:42:33.560 --> 00:42:35.560
so as they sent a spy

00:42:35.560 --> 00:42:37.560
Safiyah binti Abdul Muttalib

00:42:37.560 --> 00:42:39.560
who was the aunt of Rasulullah

