00:53:15.560 --> 00:53:17.560
he says i am Muawiyah and he picked the one next to him

00:53:17.560 --> 00:53:19.560
he says what's your name he says i am Amr ibn al-As

00:53:19.560 --> 00:53:21.560
and he was quiet no one asked him who are you

00:53:21.560 --> 00:53:23.560
because he had asked both of them

00:53:23.560 --> 00:53:25.560
Subhanallah

00:53:25.560 --> 00:53:27.560
and when he came back he told Rasulullah

00:53:27.560 --> 00:53:29.560
sallallahu alayhi wa sallam what had happened and this was

00:53:29.560 --> 00:53:31.560
also a miracle where

00:53:31.560 --> 00:53:33.560
he was very intelligent he immediately asked

00:53:33.560 --> 00:53:35.560
what's your name and what's your name and so

00:53:35.560 --> 00:53:37.560
nobody asked him what was his name may Allah

00:53:37.560 --> 00:53:39.560
sallallahu alayhi wa sallam open our doors these people

00:53:39.560 --> 00:53:41.560
thereafter were dispersed

00:53:41.560 --> 00:53:43.560
by Allah sallallahu alayhi wa sallam

00:53:43.560 --> 00:53:45.560
and verses were revealed in the whole

00:53:45.560 --> 00:53:47.560
Surah known as Surah al-Ahzab

00:53:47.560 --> 00:53:49.560
where Allah makes mention of the Hippocrates

00:53:49.560 --> 00:53:51.560
and how they had wanted

00:53:51.560 --> 00:53:53.560
to go back and Allah sallallahu alayhi wa sallam

00:53:53.560 --> 00:53:55.560
makes mention of how

00:53:55.560 --> 00:53:57.560
there were people who really felt

00:53:57.560 --> 00:53:59.560
that on this day the Muslims would not be victorious

00:53:59.560 --> 00:54:01.560
but Allah says with our

00:54:01.560 --> 00:54:03.560
power we chased them away

00:54:03.560 --> 00:54:05.560
we sent them they went back to Makkah

00:54:05.560 --> 00:54:07.560
al-Mukarramah and they had lost

00:54:07.560 --> 00:54:09.560
and inshallah tomorrow we will go through some of these

00:54:09.560 --> 00:54:11.560
verses that expose the Hippocrates

00:54:11.560 --> 00:54:13.560
and at the same time we will see what happened

00:54:13.560 --> 00:54:15.560
to Banu Qurayza those people

00:54:15.560 --> 00:54:17.560
who had sided with the enemy

00:54:17.560 --> 00:54:19.560
thinking that on that day the Muslims

00:54:19.560 --> 00:54:21.560
would never win and they broke their treaty

00:54:21.560 --> 00:54:23.560
what did the Prophet sallallahu alayhi wa sallam

00:54:23.560 --> 00:54:25.560
do to them inshallah we will see that tomorrow

00:54:25.560 --> 00:54:27.560
until then
